phrs.translation: 双加勒特球形轴承涡轮

sentences.sentence: They say it will have twin turbos and NOS but it looks to be a bit short of complete at this point.
sentences.translation: 他们说它会搭载双涡轮增压和NOS系统，但是目前看来这项工作还差一点才完成。

sentences.sentence: For turbo, it's not the better the bigger it gets - larger turbos have a longer spool up time and thus longer turbo lag.
sentences.translation: 不是越大越好-大型涡轮增压引擎有一个较长的缓冲时间，而涡轮滞后。

sentences.sentence: Turbochargers can be mounted to its own exhaust manifold but on inline engines, both turbos can be mounted on the same manifold.
sentences.translation: 涡轮增压器可以安装到自己的排气歧管但直列发动机上，都可以安装增压器在同一在静听着的松林之间。
